Module: ezobjects-mysql [top]

Copyright © 2018 Rich Lowe

Easy automatic class creation using simple configuration objects. Capable of automatically creating a matching MySQL table and generating delete(), insert(), load(), and update() methods in addition to the constructor, initializer, and getters/setters for all configured properties.
